    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（秋になると、麻奈のバースデーライブのことを思い出す）\n（遙子さんのおかげで会場は大盛り上がりだったっけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（When autumn comes‚ I remember Mana’s birthday live.）\n（Thanks to Haruko-san‚ the venue was really lively.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.5999995548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈も大いにはしゃいでいたが、少しだけ寂しそうに）\n（「琴乃にはフラれちゃった」と言っていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana was having fun too‚ but looked a little lonely）\n（and said‚ \"Kotono rejected me.\"）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4999995548,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4366.6669846,
          "startTime": 18.8666665394
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.2999995548
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.2999995548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "こうやって、{user}さんと二人きりで\n歩くのも、なんだか久しぶりですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like it's been a long time\nsince we walked like this‚ just the two of us‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "タクシーを好きなだけ使えればいいんだが\n時間に余裕があるなら経費削減ってことで……悪いな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wish we could use taxis as much as we want‚\nbut since we have time‚ let’s save on expenses… sorry about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5656008402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.7322666804
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ。{user}さんとゆっくり話せて\n私も嬉しいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. I'm happy about having time\nto chat with you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストがBIG4になってから、ずっとばたばたしてて\n最近はこういう時間もあまりなかったなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since Moon Tempest became BIG4‚ it’s been hectic‚\nand recently I haven’t had much time like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.8054184277
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "休みもなかなか取れなくて悪いな……。みんなと\nどこか遊びに行きたいなんて話にはならないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry we hardly get time off…hasn’t there been talk\nabout going out somewhere with everyone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4054192542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.8387517611
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "今はみんな、仕事が一番楽しいって感じですから\nあ。すずはこの間、遊園地に行きたいって叫んでました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ everyone feels like work is the most fun.\nOh‚ Suzu recently shouted that she wants to go to an amusement park.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}